    # "A moment later, the lights returned, and the room had become like a quiz corner."
    "一段时间后房间又亮了起来，变成了像是要开展问答比赛的布局。"

# game/r3_quiz.rpy:11
translate simplified_chinese r3_quiz_f446efa5:

    # l "First up is the quiz challenge! Get 6 out of 6 correct to continue!"
    l "「首先是问答挑战！6道题全部回答正确即可通过！」"

# game/r3_quiz.rpy:13
translate simplified_chinese r3_quiz_f5d88007:

    # l "If you miss even one...well, you don’t want to know what will happen."
    l "「如果出现哪怕一次错误…不过，你也不会想知道会发生什么吧」"

# game/r3_quiz.rpy:17
translate simplified_chinese r3_quiz_e81ee560:

    # pi "Don’t worry, Kohigashi! This first part is usually really easy!"
    pi "「没问题的，[player_last_name!t]女士！最开始的挑战一般都很简单的啦！」"

# game/r3_quiz.rpy:19
translate simplified_chinese r3_quiz_2e4695e5:

